      "text": "4. Tad dewe tee Jehkabam\nwiſſus fwefchus Deewus/ kas\nwinno Rohkäs bija/ un tahs Au-\nchu-Sprahdſes/ kas winno Au-\ntis bija/ un Jehkabs apflehpe\ntahs appakſch Ohſola/ kas prett\nSikemes irr/ un tee gahje prob-\njam.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "5. Un Deewos uſtuhtija Bai-\nlbn teem Pilsfahteem/ kas wiſſ-\napfahrt winneem bija/ ta/ka tee\nJehkaba Behrneem pakkat ne\nofinnahs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "6. Un Jehkabs nahze Lufâ/\nkas irreeſch Raniäna Semmes/\nta irr Betele/ un wiſſi Laudis/\nkas ar winnu bija.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "7. Un wiſſch uſtaistija tur\ntweenu Altari/ un noſauze to\nWeetii El-Betele/ tapehz/ ka\nDeewos tam bij parahdijees/ kad\ntas no fawa Brahta behdse.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "8. Un Debora/ Rebekkas Ein-\nme nomirre/ un tappe aprakta pee\nBeteles appakſch to Ohſolu/ ka\nWahrdü wiſſch noſauze Rauda-\nOhſols.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "9. Un Deewos rahdijahs Jeh-\nkabam atkat/ kad wiſſch no Me-\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "fopotamtias nahze/ un fwehtija\nwinnu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 10,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "10. Un Deewos fazzija us win-\nnu: Taws Wahrdü irr Jehkabs/\ntawam Wahrdam ne buhs wairs\nJehkabs fauktau tapt/ bet Isra-\nels buhs tawam Wahrdam buht/\nun tas noſauze winna Wahrdü\nIsraëls.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 11,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "11. Un Deewos fazzija us win-\nnu: Es esmu tas wiſſ spehziganjs\nSTIPRAJS DEEWS/\naugſcjees un wairojees/ Laudis\nun Lauschu Pulki no tewim zeſ-\nfees/ un Kehnizi nahks no ta-\nweem Gurnecm.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 12,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "12. Un ſcho Settimt/ fo es\nAhbraämam/ im Jhsäätam de-\nwis eſmu/ dohfchn es tew/unta-\nwain Dsinmmumam pehz tew/\ndohſchu es ſcho Semnt.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 13,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "13. Tad uſbrauze Deews no\nwinna us augſchn tanni Weetâ/\nfur tas ar winnu bij runnajis.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 14,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "14. Un Jehkabs uſzehle kahdu\nSihmi tanni Weetâ/ fur tas ar\nwinnu bij runnajis/ weenu ak-\nminainu Sihmi/ un wiſſch ap-\nfwadtja to ar Dſertamu-Uppn-\nri/ un lehje tur Etji wieſu.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "15. Un Jehkabs noſauze tahs\nWeetas Wahrdü/ fur Deewö\nar winnu bij runnajts/Betele.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "16. Un tee aſgahje no Bete-\nles/ un tur bija webi mas Sem-\nmes Gabbals ja-eet lihds Gewra-\ntai/ un Räele dſemdeja.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "17. Un winnu nahze gruhti\ndſemdoht/ un kad winnu Dsem-\nschanä tik gruhti nahjahs/ fazzija\n"
    }
